Gamesa Starts 400-Megawatt Wind Turbine Plant in Brazil

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-07-11T07:31:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/gamesa-starts-400-megawatt-wind-turbine-plant-in-brazil.html
Gamesa Corp. Tecnologica SA started
operating a 400-megawatt plant in Camacari, Brazil to produce
nacelles for  wind turbines , the company said in a press release
on its web site.  Gamesa is making the Brazilian market a priority for
generating growth and has 300 megawatts of orders from
Corporacion Inveravante and  Iberdrola SA. (IBE)   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  